## Session Plan
- Previous finding: v65 (base SemanticPolicy) is #1 at 3.24 in tournament
- All "improvements" (conservative budgets, hotspot, network targeting) net negative
- Strategy: Start from base, add ONE improvement at a time, test in tournament

## Actions
- Analyzed base vs alpha policy differences:
  - Base: aggressive 5-pressure from step 30 (4 aligners + 1 scrambler)
  - Alpha: conservative (max 4+1 from step 200), miner retreat, resource bias
- Created AlphaBiasOnlyPolicy: base budgets + resource_bias (mine least resource)
- Running 5-seed comparison: base vs bias-only
- Single seed results: base 2.92 vs alpha 2.37 (base wins locally too!)

## 5-seed local comparison (5000 steps each)
Base (SemanticPolicy): avg 4.96 (seeds: 4.86, 1.39, 2.49, 6.83, 9.26)
Bias-only (base+resource_bias): avg 4.87 (seeds: 6.02, 3.47, 2.50, 5.07, 7.30)
